Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after I got back from Mr. Braun's,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moeka and her group
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}always appeared on Friday the 13th.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did the world line change when I sent the message
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.56,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not give in to your assistant's threats. \NFollow Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}telling myself not to follow Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If so, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has Mayuri been saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will nothing happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri will die in two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've time leaped and seen it over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given what Amane-san said,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to go from the alpha \NAttractor Field — where we are now —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the beta world line, in order to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need the IBN 5100,\N to delete SERN's data on the you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the IBN 5100 that used to be at Yanabayashi Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,disappeared when the world line moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world lines moved when \Nyou sent the following D-mails:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:20.60,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma \NNo Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Lotto-6,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.22,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma \NNo Subject \N\NBuy Lotto-6 \NYou'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiryuu-san's,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urushibara-san's,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris-san's,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the one about tailing Amane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.43,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not give in to your assistant's threats. \NFollow Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you undid the one \Nabout following Amane-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attack was delayed a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you go back and undo the other D-mails,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could return to the world line \Nthat had the IBN 5100, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no scientific proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:52.39,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Made in Complex
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if there's any chance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that I suggested it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but canceling out all those D-mails...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll be pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your brain's a valuable sample, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to keep memories \Nacross world line changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've survived the time leap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should map it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't remember that\Nyou called me Kurisu... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Going in order, the next one you should undo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feyris's D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Feyris is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The UPX Arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final round of the Rai-Net ABGC just ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ABGC?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Short for the Rai-Net Access Battlers \NGrand Championship. Duh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tournament of Rai-Netters,\N from across Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just ended with her victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After Feyris sent her D-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akiba returned to only selling electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what was in the message...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who did she send it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did she send?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cat-girl is with some guy in a lab coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that she could...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape my Darkness Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Viral Attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Viral Attackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the worst kind of Rai-Netter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do anything to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were mad about losing to Feyris,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they set an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotta be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, didn't you just call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you to tell me about your D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message you sent to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A message I sent to the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this world line,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feyris doesn't remember sending a D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypothetically speaking... Hypothetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I said we built a time machine, \Nwould you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd believe anything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris just built a dimensional-transport machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's imagine that Akiba was a city filled with moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you used the time machine to change it \Nto the electronics market it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of game is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Please just answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet a moe-filled city would be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I talked to Dad about that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About opening a maid café in Akiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean May Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never even told my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, in Akiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiba had moe everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anyone else, you loved that city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once you sent that message,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole city changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you send?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.68,Sign17A,,0000,0000,0000,,Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where May Queen was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The café you wanted to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayuri, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru came all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We met here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now begin the Feyris Cup day division.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plan Code: G-B-A-C-K
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my The World's In Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of masters came in today. It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if you can't undo the D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri's life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, her life is in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to undo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri... You don't care if Mayuri dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought my dad back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after his death, ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed the past
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to prevent his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pretty face is ruined, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, princess, you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught the cat-girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My super-dangerous aura's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be seeing him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}been telling me it wants her turned black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Only one can stand at a scene's forefront,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the phoenix with black wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll make the cat-girl mine \Nwith an elegant, crazy dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And that'll be the last thing she ever sees...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you kids doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C203 is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police? I'm under arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to celebrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't see you at the UPX arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't answer your phone, \Nso I went looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun, I don't know how to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to thank me for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd gone to see the tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have work. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An IBN 5100?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know you don't have it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but where it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Hashida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the one who gave me the IBN 5100.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find the IBN 5100. And I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got it for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, you can tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He saved my life, and he really wants to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, Rumiho was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The company wasn't as big as its current size,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't collect the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, someone came and told me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they'd purchase the IBN 5100 \Nfor a huge amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how you lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of it, I was able to raise the ransom money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always kept my promises to my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how small...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(,1000)}{\a6}Papa  Rumiho
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I brought my dad back to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}after his death, ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I changed the past to prevent his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I send the D-mail, he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okarin, are you sending a D-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you do that, all of this will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I don't, Mayuri, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt that much darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they all wearing black?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Rumiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you, Kyouma... \NI mean, Okabe-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't correct yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me what you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kyouma, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Mayushii's life is in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, on my eighth birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my dad had promised to take me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But work came up... So he had to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he couldn't help it, but I was so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he didn't love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him I hated him! That I wanted him to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last time I ever spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:15.56,Sign17B,,0000,0000,0000,,Died in the crash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.35,Sign17B,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese passenger, Akiha Yukitaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent a D-mail to change that past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.43,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,We have your daughter. Ransom is 100 million yen. \NTake the Shinkansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2043)}So he wasn't in the crash,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you never brought moe culture to Akiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Akiba remained an electronics market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyr... Rumiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send that D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad died in an accident, ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what truly happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ten years have been a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how much he loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayushii is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened before the world line changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I remember what happened after, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mixed together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think I'll be able to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is real, for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be another way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I can ask Kurisu—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want to cause you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to wake up from this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me have one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I cry a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:46.72,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapping was just a joke. \NI love you, Daddy. See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world reverts to how it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will all my memories vanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories are from before and after
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world line changed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris wouldn't want to forget \Nher time with Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready, Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen my cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii says she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the only other person I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma, did you see what's on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you did, forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must remain forever sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma, why don't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "What's the it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing something perverted again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin's so bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma and Feyris fought a great darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as lovers together, in a past life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight lots of people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Feyris-san another one like Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The IBN 5100 wasn't at Yanabayashi Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ten years ago, Feyris gave it to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said it was there until last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...did it go?
